    "retreat": "OVERDUB — Temporal Evolution and Degradation-as-Architecture",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-21",
    "scripture": [
      "Scripture VII-3: Degradation Is Not Failure — It Is Memory Made Audible"
    ],
    "revelation": "Maximum wow/flutter is not an imperfection. It is a machine breathing.",
    "diagnosis": "At dub_delayWow=0.95 and dub_delayWear=0.88, the delay feedback becomes a bandpass-narrowing, pitch-wavering organism. Held notes turn into audible time. This is the signature Transcendental behavior for OVERDUB."
  },
